<font face="Comic Sans MS">And now you think
you can steal it from us?</font>

2229
01:59:19,200 --> 01:59:22,398
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You think I'm not gonna fight
to protect my home,</font>

2230
01:59:22,480 --> 01:59:24,153
<font face="Comic Sans MS">our birthright,</font>

2231
01:59:24,240 --> 01:59:26,755
<font face="Comic Sans MS">our ancestral family home?</font>

2232
01:59:29,120 --> 01:59:30,600
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That is hooey.</font>

2233
01:59:30,680 --> 01:59:32,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Harlan, he bought this place in the '80s</font>

