2237
01:59:43,600 --> 01:59:45,398
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So what do you have on me?</font>

2238
01:59:45,480 --> 01:59:47,119
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Nothing. What, attempted murder?</font>

2239
01:59:47,240 --> 01:59:49,675
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I get arson for the building
