2249
02:00:34,960 --> 02:00:36,155
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well...</font>

2250
02:00:37,320 --> 02:00:38,674
<font face="Comic Sans MS">In for a penny...</font>

2251
02:01:23,080 --> 02:01:24,196
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Shit.</font>

2252
02:02:57,400 --> 02:02:59,790
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Linda!</font>

2253
02:02:59,880 --> 02:03:02,395
