2257
02:03:15,880 --> 02:03:18,679
<font face="Comic Sans MS">From the first moment
you set foot in front of me.</font>

2258
02:03:23,920 --> 02:03:25,036
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, shit.</font>

2259
02:03:25,120 --> 02:03:28,113
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I want you to remember something
that's very important.</font>

2260
02:03:29,480 --> 02:03:30,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You won,</font>

2261
02:03:30,720 --> 02:03:33,474
<font face="Comic Sans MS">not by playing the game Harlan's way...</font>

2262
02:03:34,320 --> 02:03:35,436
<font face="Comic Sans MS">but yours.</font>

2263
02:03:37,840 --> 02:03:39,035
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You're a good person.</font>

2264
02:03:41,280 --> 02:03:42,714
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This family...</font>

2265
02:03:49,080 --> 02:03:51,197
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I should help them. Right?</font>

2266
02:03:52,120 --> 02:03:54,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I have my opinion,</font>

2267
02:03:56,120 --> 02:03:58,430
